title: 2 Bedroom, 1.75 bathroom Northview Terrace Condo in Gig Harbor
posting_body: ['2 Bedroom, 1.75 bathroom Northview Terrace Condo in Gig Harbor', 'This 2 bedroom, 1.75 bathroom upper level condo is approx.', '1,292 sq. ft and located close to downtown Gig Harbor waterfront and shops.', 'The living room offers large windows provide plenty of natural lighting.', 'Off the living room there is a decorative only fireplace and a sliding door onto the deck where you can enjoy a view of the harbor and manicured grounds.', 'The kitchen offers a refrigerator, stove, plenty of counter and cabinet space.', 'There is one full bedroom and bathroom down the hall, along with a Primary Suite, which has its own bathroom.', ' Washer and dryer are included.', 'The unit comes with one covered and one uncovered parking space and a separate storage closet.', 'Water & trash are included.', 'This is a No Pets and No Smoking property.', 'Applications are accepted only through McNally Management.', 'Apply at <URL>', 'To view a Virtual Video Tour, copy & paste link to browser:', 'https://youtu.be/aoUTMNkZuhw', '7400 Stinson Avenue, #220', 'Gig Harbor, WA 98335', 'Rent: $2,100.00/ month', 'Deposit: $2,000.00', 'Non-Refundable Application Fee $50.00/Adult', '12 month lease available', 'Available August', 'Please call for Information', 'show contact info', 'McNally Management']
